seo.meta_title: Style DROP | Step into a new style, with our fashion event | Cashrewards 20-21 July
seo.meta_description: Want to frock the boat with the latest trends and get incredible cashback when you do? Style DROP is the perfect opportunity for savvy shoppers to find a bargain with top brands like H&M, Seed Heritage, Bonds, Kiehls, Lancome and Farfetch. Coming down the catwalk July 20th-21st. Its time to get a little bit chic-y.
